# Power BI Sales Dashboard 📊

This project is a Sales Analysis Dashboard created using **Power BI**, inspired by the tutorial by [Codebasics on YouTube](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j4xlVLgsmNQ&list=PLdOKnrf8EcP2ivbQIcVuknjdlUqkoprKo&index=2).

---

## 🎯 Objective
To create an interactive dashboard that provides insights into overall sales, profit, customer segments, and regional performance using a fictional Superstore dataset.

---

## 📁 Project Files
| File | Description |
|------|-------------|
| `Attrition Project.pbix` | Final Power BI dashboard file |
| `dataset.xlsx` | Dataset used for creating the dashboard |
| `Attrition Project.pdf` | Preview of the final dashboard (PDF) |

---

## 💻 Tools Used
- Microsoft Power BI
- Excel (for data prep)

